name: Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Glen Green

details.description:
The Reebok Club C 85 Vintage (TV) Chalk Glen Green has the Reebok company logo on different shoe parts, including the front, side, and back, with the sole getting the Reebok logo as well.
 
  The Reebok Club C 85 Vintage (TV) Chalk Glen Green is available in different colorways, including chalk, paper white, and glen green. The upper material of the Club C 85 Vintage (TV) Reebok Chalk Glen Green is leather and a rubber sole sits underfoot.  
 
  The Reebok Club C 85 Vintage (TV) Chalk Glen Green was released on the 12th of February, 2021 at a retail price of $90.

name: Reebok Club C 85 White Green

details.description:
The Reebok Club C 85 White/Green comes in a white and green color scheme.

The White/Green Reebok Club C 85 adopts a classic silhouette with an upper that is constructed from durable and supple suede for breathability and comfort. The shoe features a perforated toe box for ventilation. The shoe features an EVA foam midsole, which offers responsive cushioning, impact absorption, and support. The durable rubber outsole provides stability and traction. The sneaker features a "Reebok" inscription on one side, tongue, and heel.

What we love about the Reebok Club C 85 White/Green is its stylish and refreshing colorway that combines classic elements with a modern twist. The shoe features a pristine white leather upper construction, with a white base serving as a canvas for the vibrant accents of green that adorn it, giving it a clean and timeless look. The Reebok Club C 85 White/Green was released on January 4, 2019, and sold for a retail price of $70. The Reebok Club C 85 White Green released again in 2023 and sold for a retail price of $75.

name: Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Essential Blue

details.description:
The Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Essential Blue is a classic sneaker known for its timeless design, comfort, and versatility.

This shoe features a clean and minimalist design, characterized by its predominantly white upper with blue accents. It is constructed from leather material and features a padded collar and tongue for added comfort and support. The upper of the Vintage Chalk Reebok Club C 85 also showcases a few signature design elements like the perforated detailing on the toe box and stitched overlays. The sole unit, on the other hand, is made from rubber and has a multidirectional traction pattern for improved grip. Branding details on this iteration include the Reebok logo on the heel tab, side panels, and tongue.

One thing we love about the Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Essential Blue is the padded insole for extra comfort and EVA midsole for lightweight cushioning and support. The shoes were initially released at the retail price of $85 in March 2022.

name: Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Alabaster

details.description:
The Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Alabaster takes a timeless Reebok silhouette and reintroduces it to modern audiences.

Inspired by basketball shoes from the 1980s, the Chalk Alabaster Reebok Club C 85 Vintage boasts a light and clean colorway of Chalk and Alabaster. The upper is crafted from premium leather with layered overlays and tonal stitching. Perforations across the toe box allow the foot to breathe without detracting from the retro silhouette. The EVA foam midsole provides a layer of cushioning, while the rubber outsole offers superior grip. Something that makes this sneaker stand out is the Reebok branding. For example, the lateral side panel displays "REEBOK" and the Union Jack flag and additional Reebok branding can be found on the heel, the midsole, and the tongue.

Our experts at StockX like the terrycloth lining in navy because it contributes to the sneaker’s vintage look. The Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Alabaster was released on February 7, 2022, and sold for $85.

details.description: DISCLAIMER: There are two different variations of text shown on the midsole of the Reebok Club C 85 White Sheer Grey (AR0455/100000154). The white "Reebok" text, as shown, as well as the sheer grey "Reebok" text variations are both passable under this product page.

name: Reebok Club C 85 Pump Glen Green

details.description:
The Reebok Club C 85 Pump Glen Green is a classic, streamlined, retro shoe that provides a pump to help ensure a customized fit.

This low-top sneaker features an upper with a base of smooth white leather. Three rows of perforations line the toe box, facilitating breathability and helping to enhance overall foot comfort. Smooth white leather overlays adorn the toe cap, eye stays, and heel and course across side panel. Green embroidered Reebok branding in a side-panel window matches the branding on the heel tab and a green textile stripe beneath the collar. Green and white checks appear on the tongue liner. A sail-colored eEVA foam midsole provides cushioning and rests atop a tonal outsole grooved for traction.

The detail we appreciate most on this sneaker is the bright lemon yellow button on the tongue tag that inflates or deflates the upper and lower parts of the tongue. The Reebok Club C 85 Pump Glen Green was released on May 17, 2023 for $110 retail.

name: Reebok Club C 85 Hunter X Hunter Killua
Reebok Club C Revenge Sonic the Hedgehog 3 Knuckles
Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Green (Women's)
Reebok Club C 85 JJJJound Light Grey Suede
Reebok Club C 85 Vintage Chalk Alabaster Brush Brown
Reebok Club C Stomper BAIT Astro Boy Club
Reebok Club C Maison Margiela Tan

details.description:
Reebok and Maison Margiela have worked closely in recent years to rework a bunch of classic Reebok sneakers. The Reebok Club C Maison Margiela Tan showcases what these brands are able to come up with when they mix their distinct styles together.

This Reebok Club C x Maison Margiela sneaker features an upper that is made entirely out of a singular piece of flat leather. It also has the original Club C sneaker printed on it, and this makes all the lines and curves on the sneaker stand out so much more than they would otherwise. The look is completed with a textile lining inside the sneaker and a durable rubber outsole on the bottom of it.

Our experts continue to be impressed with the different sneakers that Reebok and Maison Margiela bring back to life through their collaborations. This one, in particular, puts a whole new spin on the iconic Club C sneaker and gives it a much higher-end appearance than it once had. The Reebok Club C Maison Margiela Tan was released on June 25, 2021, for a $300 retail price.

name: Reebok Club C 85 Washed Clay
Reebok Club C 85 Pride White (2020)
Reebok Club C Revenge Vintage MANORS Chalk Red
Reebok Club C JJJJound White Olive

details.description:
JJJJound introduces a fresh olive-green color variation to the iconic Reebok Club C 85 in this Reebok Club C JJJJound White Olive.

In the JJJJound White Olive Reebok Club C collaboration, the minimalist aesthetics of the Montreal design studio are applied to this classic silhouette. The low-top sneaker showcases a white leather upper, boasting a soft terry cloth interior in an understated hue of olive green. Distinctive details encompass a nylon tongue in beige, along with the incorporation of JJJJound branding on the logo window located on the lateral side. Beneath the sneaker lies a sturdy rubber cupsole with stitched sidewall construction and an exposed foam wedge on the medial side, ensuring both durability and a distinctive look.

The standout feature of the Reebok Club C JJJJound White Olive is its luxuriously soft interior. The plush terry cloth lining in a soothing olive-green shade not only adds a touch of comfort, but also gives these sneakers a unique and cozy feel. The sneaker debuted for $150 on April 6th, 2023.

name: Reebok Club C 85 JJJJound Nubuck Core Black

details.description:
The Reebok Club C 85 JJJJound Nubuck Core Black represents a collaboration between a signature silhouette from the world-renowned sneaker company and the Montreal-based streetwear designer.

The JJJJound x Reebok Club C 85 reflects the minimalist style of JJJJound in its colorway of Unrelieved Black. The upper features a nubuck base with nubuck overlays at the toebox, quarter panel, eye stays, and heel tab. Black stitching appears at the overlay edges as well as running across the upper. Flat laces cross over a mesh tongue, while the leather sock liner provides a distinctive look and smooth feel. The sole unit features cupsole construction with an embossed pattern of dots all along the sidewall. The black rubber outsole grooved for traction completes the all-black colorway of this shoe.

What we find most delightful about this stealthy sneaker are the hits of branding. A mesh window just below the lateral eyestays features JJJJound branding. The insole sports the Reebok pinwheel and both the midsole and outsole feature embossed Reebok branding. The Reebok Club C 85 JJJJound Nubuck Core Black was released on April 6th, 2023, for a price of $160 retail.

name: Reebok Club C Revenge Vintage Vintage Chalk Collegiate Royal

details.description:
A throwback to yesteryear, the Reebok Club C Revenge Vintage Vintage Chalk Collegiate Royal tennis-inspired sneaker features vintage-style leather and exudes an old-school aesthetic and tactile experience.

The Vintage Chalk Collegiate Royal Reebok Club design has a white leather upper and is adorned with royal blue side stripes. The distinctive Reebok logo is nestled on the lateral quarter panel, featuring the classic Union Jack emblem. It features a soft terry cloth lining and a plush exposed foam tongue. The addition of a contrasting heel tab and side stripes amplifies the nostalgic charm even further. This low-top sneaker is supported by a robust rubber cupsole. It boasts an exposed EVA wedge on the medial sidewall to both durability and an authentic throwback aesthetic.

What our experts love about the Reebok Club C Revenge Vintage Vintage Chalk Collegiate Royal is its deep-rooted connection to tennis heritage. This sneaker pays homage to its tennis origins with a classic design. The sneaker was released 2nd June 2021 for $80.
